pomProject.name: ColorPicker
pomProject.description: A nice color picker using Java Swing that contains a visual color selection and input boxes to enter RGB and HSB values manually

pomProject.name: Apache Commons CLI
pomProject.description: Apache Commons CLI provides a simple API for presenting, processing and validating a Command Line Interface.

pomProject.name: Apache Commons Lang
pomProject.description: Apache Commons Lang, a package of Java utility classes for the classes that are in java.lang's hierarchy, or are considered to be so standard as to justify existence in java.lang.

pomProject.name: Apache Commons Text
pomProject.description: Apache Commons Text is a library focused on algorithms working on strings.

pomProject.name: Swing Check Box Tree
pomProject.description: A set of components for use with Swing JTrees that provide support for JCheckBox nodes.

pomProject.name: SwingX AutoComplete
pomProject.description: AutoComplete functionality for text components and combo boxes.

pomProject.name: SwingX Commons
pomProject.description: Code common to all SwingX modules.

pomProject.name: SwingX Graphics
pomProject.description: Graphics Utilities and Libraries for working with Java2D.
